DESCRIPTION:Reach out to your dealer to confirm timing and availability\n\n
 National investor call on Wednesday\, April 29th. Replay available by 6:00
 pm ET.\nIssuer: FULTON FINL CORP (FULT)\n\nDeal context:\nFulton Financial
  Corporation is conducting fixed income investor calls on April 29-30\, or
 ganized by Piper Sandler and J.P. Morgan\, ahead of a potential subordinat
 ed notes offering. Subject to market conditions\, the holding company plan
 s an SEC-registered offering of subordinated notes with expected ratings o
 f Baa2 (Moody's) and BBB(high) (Morningstar DBRS)\, placing the deal firml
 y in Investment Grade territory. No size\, tenor\, or pricing details have
  been disclosed at this mandate stage\, with Piper Sandler coordinating lo
 gistics for the investor calls.
